# Secrets / runtime-mounted paths. .env.local and config/jwt are bind-mounted at
# runtime by docker-compose, never baked into the image — so the Dockerfile must
# NOT run `composer dump-env prod` (it would compile these placeholders into a
# .env.local.php that shadows the mount). See ../codetrics-lab docker-compose.yml.
.env.local
.env.local.php
.env.*.local
config/jwt
*.log
README.md
